{"build_type":"library","description":"As-completed per-function compile worker. The work item JSON IS a self-contained one-function module {struct_definitions, module_globals, function_definitions:{one fn}, objdir} produced by the assessor; everything needed crosses the JSON bridge (no shared globals, no files). Decodes it in this worker's own arena, sets the compiler module context from it, lowers+renders JUST that one function into one objlib object in objdir via render-primitive-library-inside-object-files, returns {ok:1}. Per-worker arena holds only one function's lowering -> replaces the whole-library compile that ballooned one worker to ~1.24GB. Pure body; the as-completed runner does exit-and-notify.","module_name":"compile-one-function-from-work-item","package_name":"compile-one-function-from-work-item","function_definitions":{"compile-one-function-from-work-item":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"item","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"z_cache_reset","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"global_write","name":"g_disc_state","value":"z_cache_reset"},{"instruction_type":"global_write","name":"g_err_catalog_state","value":"z_cache_reset"},{"instruction_type":"global_write","name":"g_val_catalog","value":"z_cache_reset"},{"instruction_type":"global_write","name":"g_sha256_h_init_table","value":"z_cache_reset"},{"instruction_type":"global_write","name":"g_sha256_k_table","value":"z_cache_reset"},{"instruction_type":"global_write","name":"g_statbuf","value":"z_cache_reset"},{"instruction_type":"global_write","name":"g_linkbuf","value":"z_cache_reset"},{"instruction_type":"global_write","name":"g_rellinkbuf","value":"z_cache_reset"},{"instruction_type":"global_write","name":"g_dirent_buffer","value":"z_cache_reset"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"one","variable_type":"i64",